                </p>
                <p>
                    Remember, CT Scans and MRI may detect some traces of endometrial tissue but not others.
                    Misdiagnosis is pervasive in women's health, so never hesitate to ask for a second opinion.

                    By working closely with your healthcare providers,
                    it is possible to maintain a good quality of life through personalized care and support.
                </p>
